• 100kw solar installation – huge benefits in running costs
• Huge power supply (800A stc)
• Super fast ‘Gig city’ internet connection
• Zoned Urban Core in the Mawson Innovation precinct
• Extensive drive through canopy
• Secured 4,260sqm* site with 44 on site car parks and building expansion capacity or more yard if required
• Excellent shopping and cafes within walking distance
